ingredients.ingredient: 2 ounces VELVEETA®, cut into 24 small cubes
4 OSCAR MAYER Beef Franks, each cut into 6 pieces
½ cup GREY POUPON Savory Honey Mustard

cookingTips: Prepare muffin mix according to package directions, then fold in cheese and franks
Fill muffin cups only halfway so toppings don't overflow during baking
Serve warm with mustard for dipping for the complete corn dog experience
enrichment.coachingPrompt: This is a fun, kid-friendly take on classic corn dogs using muffin format. Interested in creative transformations?
